Package org.springframework.integration.helper.config

Class NatsStreamCollectionProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.integration.helper.config.NatsStreamCollectionProperties
  • public class NatsStreamCollectionProperties
extends Object
    Config Properties Collection of Streams

    Can be used as Configuration properties bean to detect the stream properties(Map of streams) provided in the below format <properties_prefix>.nats.<workflow>.stream <properties_prefix>.nats.<workflow>.subject

    Eg:

    <properties_prefix>.nats.notification.stream=notification <properties_prefix>.nats.notification.subject=notification-email <properties_prefix>.nats.sttl.stream=settlement <properties_prefix>.nats.sttl.subject=settlement-tc
